{"tid":469778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強國科技] 強國製造2TB行動硬碟 拆解後裡面竟是......","createTime":"2017-11-15T16:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T16:26:05.000Z","uid":43189,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e25d411f8fab41ac4cb1ac2009d9cd12c448b6","tid":469778,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:00:08.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一名土耳其網友透過購物網站，購買一個知名品牌的2TB行動硬碟，該硬碟為「中國製造」，網友將硬碟拿起發現內部有異，因此對它進行拆解，不料裡頭竟然塞了一張容量不到2TB的晶片。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其網友將影片PO在影音網站「LiveLeak」，網友在影片裡指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">透過全球速賣通（aliexpress）</span>購買該中國製造的名牌行動硬碟，包裝註明容量有2TB且保固3年，但進行拆解後，一個USB晶片，容量根本不到2TB，賣家為了增加重量，還在裡頭塞了兩根大大的螺釘。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其網友上網爬文後，發現在2011年也有一個類似的案例，當時有名苦主購買容量500GB的行動硬碟，打開後裡面只有一個容量128MB的USB晶片；土耳其網友認為，「如果你想從中國購買電腦零件，請三思」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZbyVRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZbyVRz.jpg&h=18f9575c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2253559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2253559&d=wRYxnbutjtFT%2FkEIN6DJLIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=aacee423\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2253559&h=38555f57\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2253559</a>"},{"pid":"afed88bc074acef9f901846be8325a03788c6970","tid":469778,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67232b7964ffb313f3c7dd756996318139e9bd0a","tid":469778,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"十幾年前， usb 已係，16G 就比個 1G既你之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af88d2cf459d9b2be8c53